{"tid":141462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【特首選戰】入唔到閘嬲嬲豬？ 葉劉：新民黨再定位或「無咁建制」","createTime":"2017-03-03T02:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T03:25:24.000Z","uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2048f2252bc1843fafb9959dfc78a9188b98934b","tid":141462,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:48:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170303/56378461\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170303%2F56378461&d=vE0XmFSztYUmu7sR0UJCJDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=e35fb3be\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170303%2F56378461&h=8a74c677\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170303/56378461</a><br />\n<br />\n再一次因為未能取得足夠提名票選特首的新民主黨席葉劉淑儀，今早在電台節目中表示會繼續領導新民黨，但她透露待特首選舉結束後，新民黨將重新思考定位，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「喺建制派內要企喺咩位置」，日後可能「無咁建制」</span></strong>，要更加獨立及敢言。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉稱，重新定位是基於民情考慮，她<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>自言不會偏向泛民，因為雙方始終有基本分歧</strong></span>，但認為經過今次特首選舉與泛民的溝通得到改善。她稱宣佈結束選舉工程後首次回到立法會，獲泛民議員熱烈支持，有人讚她的選舉工程做得好，「黃碧雲仲攬住我」，相反建制派則表現尷尬，只拍她膊頭，「叫我休息一下，睇開啲」。<br />\n<br />\n主持人追問<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>日後作風是否會接近自由黨，葉劉就指自由黨一向敢言，但始終有商界包袱，新民黨政綱則較重邏輯和理念分析</strong></span>，兩黨可以各有各做。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直接同大少合併啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b526ab9de4a0e39fabd2870c5b19df872dbf26","tid":141462,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:50:58.000Z","msg":"做左建制棄婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6972137e8ce56367f585cd5061f93c4498dfc7f","tid":141462,"uid":21896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T02:58:54.000Z","msg